<div class='talk-subsection'>
<div class='talk-top__details'>
<p class='talk-description' lang='en'>
When game designer Jane McGonigal found herself bedridden and suicidal following a severe concussion, she had a fascinating idea for how to get better. She dove into the scientific research and created the healing game, SuperBetter. In this moving talk, McGonigal explains how a game can boost resilience â€” and promises to add 7.5 minutes to your life.
</p>
